T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Energy.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind energy forms and transfer) Tj
T*
(between systems.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct physical reasoning process step by step instead of jumping to the) Tj
T*
(answer.) Tj
T*
